lead_paragraph: Jang Ha-na sank a short eagle putt on the last and immediately broke into a Beyonce-inspired shimmy to celebrate her second win of the season with a brilliant four-shot triumph at the HSBC Women's Champions on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Jang Dances Clear of Rivals to Win in Singapore
